sentence: Looking at options trading activity among components of the Russell 3000 index, there is noteworthy activity today in LegacyTexas Financial Group Inc (Symbol: LTXB), where a total volume of 1,544 contracts has been traded thus far today, a contract volume which is representative of approximately 154,400 underlying shares (given that every 1 contract represents 100 underlying shares).
That number works out to 79.7% of LTXB's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 193,835 shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $45 strike call option expiring July 21, 2017 , with 1,431 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 143,100 underlying shares of LTXB.
